name: Fall Of A Jedi
Lore: 'The blow, when it came, was lightning swift and fatal. But Qui-Gon''s death gave new life to his former Padawan.',
Text: 'If your Jedi was just defeated in lightsaber combat, you may either: Reveal a Dark Jedi''s combat cards and place one in opponent''s Lost Pile (return others). OR Place Qui-Gon out of play and take [Episode I] Obi-Wan into hand from Lost Pile or Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
